      • streamOutputToGeoServer

        public abstract void streamOutputToGeoServer(String username,
                                             String password,
                                             String url,
                                             String workspace,
                                             String coverageStore,
                                             String srs)
        Stream output files to a GeoServer instance. Currently only GeoTIFF files can be streamed to GeoServer.
        Parameters:
        username - The username to authenticate on the GeoServer instance with.
        password - The password to authenticate on the GeoServer instance with. WARNING: the password will be stored in plain text.
        url - The URL of the GeoServer instance. The web interface should be at {url}/web.
        workspace - The name of the workspace to upload the file to. If the workspace doesn't exist it will be created.
        coverageStore - The name of the coverage store to upload the file to. If the coverage store doesn't exist it will be created.
        srs - The declared spatial reference system of the uploaded file. If not provided the uploaded coverage will not be enabled.

      • addAttachment

        public abstract String addAttachment(String filename,
                                     String contents)
        Add a file attachment to the project. Attachments can be used anywhere a filename would be used.
        Parameters:
        filename - The name of the file to attach. Must be a valid Windows filename.
        contents - The file contents. Must still be valid if streamed to a file with UTF-8 encoding.
        Returns:
        Will return false if the filename is not valid, otherwise the URL to use as the filename when referencing the attachment will be returned.
